---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PCB Layout">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="reveal text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">PCB Layout</h1>

      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy mb-4">
          ntronIQ use cutting edge technologies and industry leading software for PCB layouts.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy mb-4">
          We can provide all the necessary files to enable the PCB to be manufactured from the customer's preferred supplier, or we can source and supply PCBs as required - including prototypes and full production quantities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy mb-4">
          PCBs are designed to meet the budget constraints for the customer's product.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy">
          All Manufacturability and testability requirements are incorporated into the final design. Test rigs can also be developed in order to automate testing of PCBs for high volume manufacture.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="reveal text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">3D Modelling</h2>

      <div class="reveal">
        <img
          src="/images/Subwoofer.png"
          alt="3D PCB Model"
          class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6"
        />
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy">
          3D Modelling ensures correct component placement and mechanical compatibility.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
